<title xml:lang="en" type="complete" ref="LIT2906RepCh187">To St Peter and Paul</title>
<incipit xml:lang="gez">ሰላም፡ ለዝክረ፡ ስምክሙ፡ ዘአልባስጥሮስ፡ አፈው።</incipit>
